        {
            "title": "印度稱到下月有望與美國敲定協議 以下調對等關稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"印度稱到下月有望與美國敲定協議 以下調對等關稅\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rbl_HpCNc5evMb_rVPNb9g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/ad357d50-cd35-11f0-bfff-1e0146c2252a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">印度稱到下月有望與美國敲定協議 以下調對等關稅</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%A8%B1%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E5%B0%8D%E7%AD%89%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-111622566.html",
