            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "紐約時報稱川普和委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅討論潛在會晤事宜",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據《紐約時報》報導，美國總統川普上周與委內瑞拉領導人<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:尼古拉斯·馬杜羅;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/尼古拉斯·馬杜羅\">尼古拉斯·馬杜羅</a>通話，雙方討論了潛在會面事宜。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導引述多名知情人士消息稱，雙方仍未就舉行會面作出任何安排。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普政府近期將委內瑞拉領導層列為外國恐怖組織。過去數周，美國以打擊涉嫌販毒的船隻為由在海上發動多次打擊後，不斷加強在該地區的軍事存在，並威脅將對委內瑞拉本土實施攻擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普一直試圖孤立馬杜羅政權並實施了一系列激進行動，美國稱這些行動旨在阻斷毒品流入美國。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3cec85c9-e3e6-3d0c-a66e-4235ba3f7600-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump and Maduro Discussed a Possible Meeting, NYT Reports</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%92%8C%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E7%BE%85%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C-195710207.html",
